{"tid":2220753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普要求拜登在辯論前後要接受藥檢","createTime":"2020-09-28T01:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T07:44:20.000Z","uid":28765,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c003d8509afe4f6860e12bd8cb32c6aefddc0e9c","tid":2220753,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T01:27:29.000Z","msg":"美國的總統大選首場電視辯論，將於當地星期二舉行，爭取連任的美國總統特朗普，要求對手民主黨候選人拜登在辯論之前或之後，接受藥物檢測。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在社交網站發文認為，拜登的辯論表現一直都不穩定，質疑是服用藥物所造成的差異，又表示自己亦同意接受藥物檢測。74歲的特朗普數月前開始批評77歲的拜登的精神狀態，經常將拜登形容成「昏昏欲睡的拜登」，最近幾星期也多次暗示對方可能服用不明藥物來提升表現，但他並未提供任何證據。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551947-20200928.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551947-20200928.htm&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=84c3b098\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551947-20200928.htm&h=00f634bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551947-20200928.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3d043f9756d59681d176608d76c0a099f62dc7d5","tid":2220753,"uid":346806,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T01:34:05.000Z","msg":"辯論都啪藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85955d5ab7d328aebee20604a816bb10ecead4ca","tid":2220753,"uid":270220,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T01:34:31.000Z","msg":"等侵侵精彩表演<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n侵侵唔洗食藥都好有energy<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a7648db7a51bcc8dee088877611bcb478a5e48","tid":2220753,"uid":82359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d043f9756d59681d176608d76c0a099f62dc7d5","tid":2220753,"uid":346806,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T01:34:05.000Z","msg":"辯論都啪藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor